graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        Controller[DSPO Controller Manager]
        Webhook[Admission Webhook]
        Controller -->|validates/mutates| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Per-DSPA Instance Components"
        APIServer[API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP, 8887/TCP gRPC]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent]
        ScheduledWorkflow[Scheduled Workflow Controller]
        WorkflowController[Workflow Controller<br/>v2/Argo only]
        MariaDB[(MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP)]
        Minio[Minio<br/>9000/TCP S3]
        MLUI[ML Pipelines UI]
        MLMDgRPC[ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP]
        MLMDEnvoy[ML Metadata Envoy<br/>9090/TCP]

        APIServer -->|reads/writes| MariaDB
        APIServer -->|stores artifacts| Minio
        PersistenceAgent -->|syncs metadata| MariaDB
        PersistenceAgent -->|watches workflows| K8sAPI
        ScheduledWorkflow -->|creates runs| APIServer
        ScheduledWorkflow -->|queries| MariaDB
        MLMDgRPC -->|persists| MariaDB
        MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies| MLMDgRPC
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        DSPACR[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
        ArgoWorkflows[Argo Workflows<br/>v2 only]
        TektonPipelines[Tekton Pipelines<br/>v1 only]
        ExternalDB[(External Database<br/>3306/5432 TCP)]
        ExternalS3[External S3<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        CertManager[cert-manager/<br/>Service CA]
    end

    subgraph "ODH Platform"
        ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        ODHOperator[opendatahub-operator]
        Elyra[Elyra]
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| DSPACR
    DSPACR -->|watched by| Controller
    Controller -->|creates/manages| APIServer
    Controller -->|creates/manages| PersistenceAgent
    Controller -->|creates/manages| ScheduledWorkflow
    Controller -->|creates/manages| WorkflowController
    Controller -->|creates/manages| MariaDB
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Minio
    Controller -->|creates/manages| MLUI
    Controller -->|creates/manages| MLMDgRPC
    Controller -->|creates/manages| MLMDEnvoy

    Controller -->|watches resources| K8sAPI
    Controller -->|provisions certs| CertManager
    APIServer -->|creates workflows| ArgoWorkflows
    APIServer -->|creates pipelines| TektonPipelines

    APIServer -.->|optional| ExternalDB
    APIServer -.->|optional| ExternalS3

    ODHOperator -->|deploys| Controller
    ODHDashboard -->|UI integration| APIServer
    Elyra -->|submits pipelines| APIServer

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style APIServer fill:#4a90e2
    style PersistenceAgent fill:#4a90e2
    style ScheduledWorkflow fill:#4a90e2
    style WorkflowController fill:#4a90e2
    style DSPACR fill:#f5a623
    style K8sAPI fill:#999
    style ArgoWorkflows fill:#999
    style TektonPipelines fill:#999
    style CertManager fill:#999
    style ExternalDB fill:#e8e8e8
    style ExternalS3 fill:#e8e8e8
    style ODHDashboard fill:#7ed321
    style ODHOperator fill:#7ed321
    style Elyra fill:#7ed321
    style MariaDB fill:#bd10e0
    style Minio fill:#bd10e0
